                <h3>Screening Guidelines</h3>
                <div class="resource-item">
                    <h4>Prostate Cancer Screening</h4>
                    <p>Discuss with your doctor starting at age 50, or earlier if you have risk factors.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="resource-item">
                    <h4>Testicular Self-Examination</h4>
                    <p>Perform monthly self-exams to check for any lumps or changes.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="resource-item">
                    <h4>Colonoscopy</h4>
                    <p>Recommended starting at age 45 for average-risk individuals.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
